Package lab2

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICourse
    Interface to provide methods for implementation by the abstract Course subclass, and by extension the specific Course types.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdvancedJavaCourse
    This class implements ICourse, extends Course and inherits the Course constructor, including prerequisites.
    Course
    This abstract class implements the methods from ICourse and provides the specific Course types with getter/setter methods and properties.
    DisplayUtility
    This class is to act as the display output utility for this program.
    IntroJavaCourse
    This class implements ICourse, extends Course and inherits the Course constructor, including prerequisites.
    IntroToProgrammingCourse
    This class implements ICourse, extends Course and inherits the Course constructor without prerequisites, leaving that field null.
    Startup
    Startup method to demonstrate Course subclasses and displayUtility class.
